                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={cloud.src} alt="Value Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Direct-to-Cloud Storage</p>
                            <p>Your critical business information is safely stored offsite, helping protect you from local issues like hardware failures or natural disasters.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={backup.src} alt="Management Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Customized Backup Plans</p>
                            <p>Prospector works with you to create backup and data retention policies that fit your unique business needs. There is no one-size-fits-all approach</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={disaster.src} alt="Customizable Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold lh-sm">Disaster Recovery Assistance</p>
                            <p class="fs-6">In the event of a major incident, a dedicated team guides you through the process of restoring systems, helping you minimize downtime and stress.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={local.src} alt="Customizable Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold lh-sm">Bring Your Own Local Storage</p>
                            <p class="fs-6">Quarterly restore tests ensure that if something goes wrong, you can quickly get your data back and keep your business on track.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={health.src} alt="Defense Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Backup Health Reports</p>
                            <p>You will receive regular reports on the health of your backups, giving you peace of mind that everything is working as it should.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={file.src} alt="Focus Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">On-Demand File Recovery</p>
                            <p>If you need to retrieve specific files, we make it simple and fast, so your team can continue operating smoothly.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={guide.src} alt="Customizable Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p class="fs-4 fw-bold lh-sm">Expert Guidance and Support</p>
                            <p class="fs-6">Knowledgeable Prospector staff are always on hand to answer questions, offer advice, and make sure your backup strategy evolves with your business.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Text Section -->
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4 display-5">A LASTING INVESTMENT FOR YOUR BUSINESS</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 24px;">
                        By investing in Backup and Disaster Recovery, you’re not just protecting data—you’re protecting the future of your business.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={downtime.src} alt="Protection Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Reduce Downtime</p>
                            <p>Quickly recover from setbacks so your team can get back to work, serving customers without prolonged interruptions.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={moneyShield.src} alt="Value Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Protect Revenue and Reputation</p>
                            <p>Prevent costly losses and maintain your credibility. Reliable backups help ensure you don’t lose vital information that could undermine customer trust.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={architecture.src} alt="Management Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Minimize Uncertainty</p>
                            <p>Know that if something goes wrong, you have a plan in place to restore your data and keep moving forward. This peace of mind lets you concentrate on the bigger picture.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={safeguard.src} alt="Defense Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Safeguard Your Hard Work</p>
                            <p>Your business data—documents, customer records, and project files—is the result of time, effort, and investment. Backups ensure that this invaluable information is never lost.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center mb-4">
                        <div class="col-3 text-center">
                            <img src={laptopBadge.src} alt="Focus Icon" class="img-fluid rounded">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-9">
                            <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Stay Compliant and Secure</p>
                            <p>Many industries require that you keep accurate records. By backing up and swiftly recovering your data, you help meet regulatory standards and demonstrate that you take data protection seriously</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row align-items-center">
